sequenceDiagram
 autonumber
 participant C as Component
 participant H as Hook (useListings)
 participant Q as TanStack Query
 participant S as Service
 participant AX as Axios + Interceptors
 participant API as Backend API
 C->>H: useCreateDraft() / useQuery
 H->>Q: useMutation / useQuery(queryKey)
 Q->>S: ListingService.createDraft(data)
 S->>AX: apiRequest(PATHS.xxx, payload)
 Note over AX: gắn accessToken
 AX->>API: HTTP request
 API-->>AX: response / 401
 alt 401 hết hạn token
 AX->>API: refreshToken (dedup)
 API-->>AX: token mới → retry
 end
 AX-->>S: ApiResponse<T>
 S-->>Q: data (typed)
 Q-->>H: data · isLoading · error
 H->>Q: onSuccess → invalidateQueries
 H-->>C: re-render
